message: Aim for a score of 80! Most high-value items follow a pattern: combine a protein + vegetable, then use the 'stove' (this usually gives 60). After that, combine the cooked item with a 'grain' item to reach 80. The combination of 'cooked fish salad' (raw fish + lettuce + stove) and 'cooked soaked wheat' (wheat + water + stove) yields 100 points! Bread can often be replaced by cooked soaked wheat. Good luck!
